user.biography:
Traveling around the world with my family.🧔🏻👩🏻👦🏻👧🏻🐶
Share real travel experiences only! ✌️ Follow me to get my secrets on stays, food and hidden gems.

node.text:
Those mesmerizing days in Santorini with @andronis_arcadia. ✨💦☀️Tag someone you’d love to travel there with. 👆
📍: Santorini, Greece 

•
#roomwithaview #beautifuldestinations #tlpicks #iamatraveler #voyaged #greekislands #forbestravelguide #hellofrom #santorini #greece

What’s a day like in St. Moritz when staying with @grandhotelkronenhof. 🇨🇭✨🏠🚞🏔💦🍹🍰 
Tag someone you’d love to experience these in Switzerland with. 👆
📍: St. Moritz/Pontresina, Switzerland 

1. Breakfast with a view (on the balcony of Diavolezza Suite) 
2. Take a panoramic train from Pontresina to Alp Grüm
3. Wander around Lago Bianco (Station: Ospizio Bernina)
4. Ride gonolda up to see Diavolezza Glacier (Station: Bernina Diavolezza)
5. Hike to Morteratsch Glacier (Station: Morteratsch)
6. Swim and relax in the pool/spa area with a view
7. Sip some cocktails with a view at Kronenhof Summer Lounge 
8. Dinner at Grand Restaurant
9. Enjoy the extravagant dessert buffet at the Grand Restaurant 

•
#roomwithaview #voyaged #shotoniphone #beautifuldestinations #TLPicks #iamatraveler #cntraveler #stmoritz #switzerland #inlovewithswitzerland #forbestravelguide #pontresina #grandhotelkronenhof
